stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> MaybeVersion1 : UUID UUID([long mostSigBits], [long leastSigBits])
    [*] --> NonVersion1 : UUID randomUUID()
    [*] --> NonVersion1 : UUID nameUUIDFromBytes([byte[] name])
    [*] --> MaybeVersion1 : UUID fromString([String name])

    MaybeVersion1 --> MaybeVersion1 : long getLeastSignificantBits()
    MaybeVersion1 --> MaybeVersion1 : long getMostSignificantBits()
    MaybeVersion1 --> MaybeVersion1 : int version()
    MaybeVersion1 --> MaybeVersion1 : int variant()
    MaybeVersion1 --> MaybeVersion1 : long timestamp()
    MaybeVersion1 --> MaybeVersion1 : int clockSequence()
    MaybeVersion1 --> MaybeVersion1 : long node()
    MaybeVersion1 --> MaybeVersion1 : String toString()
    MaybeVersion1 --> MaybeVersion1 : int hashCode()
    MaybeVersion1 --> MaybeVersion1 : boolean equals([Object obj])
    MaybeVersion1 --> MaybeVersion1 : int compareTo([UUID val])

    NonVersion1 --> NonVersion1 : long getLeastSignificantBits()
    NonVersion1 --> NonVersion1 : long getMostSignificantBits()
    NonVersion1 --> NonVersion1 : int version()
    NonVersion1 --> NonVersion1 : int variant()
    NonVersion1 --> NonVersion1 : String toString()
    NonVersion1 --> NonVersion1 : int hashCode()
    NonVersion1 --> NonVersion1 : boolean equals([Object obj])
    NonVersion1 --> NonVersion1 : int compareTo([UUID val])

    note right of MaybeVersion1
        timestamp(), clockSequence(), node() may throw UnsupportedOperationException
        if this UUID is not a version 1 (time-based) UUID.
        Version is determined by constructor bits or parsed string.
    end note

    note right of NonVersion1
        Created via randomUUID() (version 4) or nameUUIDFromBytes() (version 3).
        timestamp(), clockSequence(), node() are forbidden and always throw
        UnsupportedOperationException for non-version-1 UUIDs.
    end note
